            #<Introduction/Features>

                ################################################################################################<off>

                ## By Jim Raven                                                                                #<off>

                ## Makes all vendors Great By changing whites to blues and greens to purples                   #<off>

                ## Features                                                                                    #<off>

                ## Weapon vendors Now have a 10% chance at legendary IOTD Else Purple                          #<off>

                ## Health vendors Now have a 10% chance at legendary IOTD Else Purple                          #<off>

                ## Grenade vendors Now have a 10% chance at legendary IOTD Else Purple                         #<off>

                ## Blue Have been Revmoved from Item of they Day And purple have 90% of Being IOTD             #<off>

                ################################################################################################<off>
